What you need to know:

Kitale is suitable for the production of many crops, from horticulture to pasture. However, the choice of crops to grow depends on a number of issues, with market being one of them.Chilli farming is surely a profitable venture since the plants have a good market. They are rich in vitamins A, B and C as well as minerals.Yield for chillies is 1,000-3,000kg per acre but higher yields can be obtained under good management.